# LLM Model Catalog Edits (TS-21)

When editing [llm-model-catalog.json](../../config/llm-model-catalog.json) or its [JSON Schema](../../config/schemas/llm-model-catalog.schema.json):

1. Keep catalog aligned with [TECH_STACK_LLM_MODEL_CATALOG.md](../../docs/decisions/TECH_STACK_LLM_MODEL_CATALOG.md) (TS-21 ADR)
2. Update [OPENAI_PROMPT_GUIDANCE.md](../../docs/OPENAI_PROMPT_GUIDANCE.md) when `prompting.*` fields change
3. Same commit: both READMEs if customer-facing model IDs or tiers change — see [documentation-sync.mdc](./documentation-sync.mdc)
4. Do not bypass Wall-Bounce constitution for routing/analysis changes affecting production behavior

Related: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) · [OPENAI_MODEL_MATRIX.md](../../docs/OPENAI_MODEL_MATRIX.md)
